main event: A light object was sighted moving parallel to the horizon at high speed near Nandi, Honolulu/Canton in 1962.
interesting points: The light object was a blue-white color.
The object was sighted by two pilots at their four o'clock position.
The object was moving at a high speed and disappeared over the horizon.
The object was estimated to be 192 to 232 miles away.
The case was listed as having insufficient data for evaluation.
